      "id": "PopularPost13465",
      "post_content": "Akroma has two cards, and they're both awesome. Hard to say if I like the Wrath or Fury version better-Angel of Wrath has haste, vigilance, and first strike but Angel of Fury can increase her power to insane levels and kill you with trample damage (or lay waste to all of your blockers). Sad part is that comparing them in an actual game would be difficult at best since they have protection from each other. Still, awesome cards.",
